There are just 15 pawn structures that may arrise from common opennings. It is not many, I expected more combinations. I am learning the first one and books tell me to try to achieve f4-f5 and force black to exchange ... gxf5 followed by exf5. If the goal is achieved, white should be able to produce passer.
